{"tid":1881974,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"習帝同武漢市長鬥射波，邊個贏？","createTime":"2020-02-16T02:21:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T17:00:43.000Z","uid":274161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1f4398a2482385b35c27b935c872c62cceb87103","tid":1881974,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T02:21:32.000Z","msg":"2月12日，武漢漢網發社評《何不給武漢市長暖暖心》，認為12月時市長已經上報疫情，中央也派專家調研並有初步結論，市長已經跟足指示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FgHVygg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFgHVygg.jpg&h=d151e96d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2月15日，求是網刊登習帝2月3日對武漢肺炎的工作指示，開篇就話自己1月7日對疫情防控工作提出要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fQNFKoa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfQNFKoa.jpg&h=ebd33bf6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efc594436aab9eecda8f26e965241de57a19a62a","tid":1881974,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T02:22:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">君要臣死，臣不得不死</span></span>"},{"pid":"489cd9e38e4099e00786d2e17f30e4a7d16268d4","tid":1881974,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T02:23:16.000Z","msg":"武漢起義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578b2b810f347e091caa4a23f61bc10e4f39f97c","tid":1881974,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T02:24:25.000Z","msg":"武漢書記去左邊"},{"pid":"82fbb3b7aba1c4cbc3f623a0a0350dba785fa4b2","tid":1881974,"uid":111153,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T02:24:38.000Z","msg":"習總好心無能力就唔好學人大權在握 而家做乜都要請示你 唔問過你又驚秋後清算 點知你條on9做埋咁多on9決定 之後做咗又唔敢認"},{"pid":"b457b50017